{"tid":1448423,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"引狗去美國領事館有冇得諗？","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:32:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:28:28.000Z","uid":281892,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"35bfcd7fd8d92a9e38b9215c414f8c1547c7c5d0","tid":1448423,"uid":281892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:32:15.000Z","msg":"好撚絕望！<br />\n以現在既不平等戰力，我地再頂唔到幾耐<br />\n呢鋪真係要靠外國勢力！<br />\n<br />\n引狗去美國領事館，<br />\n等佢地放彈，<br />\n搞鳩到領事館，迫美國地出手，<br />\n有冇得諗？"},{"pid":"1b13551ecf18f4597b64081b6f253eabc5d7bbf9","tid":1448423,"uid":281892,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:32:56.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"bbb8da085a4c689f16647e6316be5836bd5afa0b","tid":1448423,"uid":134178,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:34:20.000Z","msg":"手足唔該幫幫手<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812 1PM起，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，唔係我們既責任，係因為機場唔夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場"},{"pid":"a6de46a5ef4be25db0118b345e2c2484caedf9d6","tid":1448423,"uid":281892,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:34:36.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"1cdabac6e27a523ef0096085961e5b3f4f3d88c3","tid":1448423,"uid":114123,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:36:31.000Z","msg":"美國領事館隔離係禮賓府 點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40375c45eeaed9f193f3d31b55980d6f7110ab1f","tid":1448423,"uid":131789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:38:26.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"fff176253057e97006e9be43d67879d8d822de11","tid":1448423,"uid":281892,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:39:40.000Z","msg":"我地要真。外國勢力介入呀！"},{"pid":"4cec13d24f017273cfd16f8be7e68e7620fe85f0","